                        Our portfolio encompasses corporate events and dinners, social events, exquisite parties and even on-the-road shows and events. Our client lists spans several industries and they include: <strong>Opa William (Night Of A Thousand Laughs), AY, I Go Dye, I Go Save, Ecobank, Diamond Bank, Globacom, MTN, MTV Base and Dangote.</strong>
                    </p>

